<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<subsection xml:id="student_learning_outcomes" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Student Learning Outcomes</title>
  <p>
    After successful completion of this course, students will be able to:
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>
        understand the concepts and perform the calculations concerning trigonometric
functions,
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
        solve right triangles and general triangles,
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
        apply, verify, and solve trigonometric identities and equations,
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
        understand and apply inverse trigonometric functions,
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
        understand the connections between trigonometry and complex numbers
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </p>
</subsection>
